---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn about New Life House of Glory's mission, vision, and leadership team. Discover our heart for spreading the gospel worldwide.">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-primary-800 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About Our Ministry</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Discover our heart for God, our mission to the world, and the family God has called together at New Life House of Glory.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Mission -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Our Mission</h2>
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-700 italic mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          "Go into all the world and preach the gospel to all creation."
        </blockquote>
        <cite class="text-lg text-primary-600 font-semibold">— Mark 16:15</cite>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-8 leading-relaxed">
          This verse is the foundation of everything we do at New Life House of Glory. We believe God has called 
          every believer to be part of His great commission—sharing the life-changing message of Jesus Christ 
          with people in our community and around the world.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

 <!-- Our Vision -->
<section class="pt-24 pb-32 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Vision</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      We envision a world where every person has heard the gospel and experienced God's love. 
      Our vision is to raise up disciples who are passionate about Jesus, equipped for ministry, 
      and committed to reaching the lost.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-left max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="ml-4 text-gray-700">
          Building strong believers through biblical teaching and discipleship
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="ml-4 text-gray-700">
          Reaching our local community with practical acts of love and service
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="ml-4 text-gray-700">
          Supporting global missions and church planting efforts worldwide
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-20"></div>

  <!-- Leadership -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Guided by Grace</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 max-w-md mx-auto">
      <!-- Pastor Image -->
      <img 
        src="/images/pastor.jpg" 
        alt="Pastor John Smith" 
        class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
      >

      <div class="p-6 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Pastor Suresh</h3>

        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Pastor Suresh has been faithfully serving in ministry for over 25 years, with a deep passion for sharing God’s Word and nurturing spiritual growth in the lives of others.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



  <!-- History -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Our Story</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-gray-600">
        <p class="text-center text-xl mb-8 text-gray-700">
          New Life House of Glory was born out of a vision to create a church where people from all walks of life 
          could encounter God's love and be equipped to fulfill the Great Commission.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-xl">
          <p class="mb-6">
            Founded in 2008 by Pastor John and Sarah Smith, our church began as a small home group with just 
            12 people who shared a passion for reaching the lost and making disciples. What started in a living room 
            has grown into a vibrant community of believers committed to spreading the gospel both locally and globally.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6">
            From the beginning, we've held fast to the biblical mandate found in Mark 16:15: "Go into all the world 
            and preach the gospel to all creation." This verse continues to guide every aspect of our ministry, 
            from our Sunday services to our community outreach programs to our support of missionaries around the world.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, we continue to grow not just in numbers, but in spiritual maturity and missional impact. 
            We believe our best days are ahead as we trust God to use us for His glory in these last days.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>